regen.new_specification: The system shall automatically generate conversion-related metadata for storage in the converted files when user input is not provided.
The system shall automatically generate conversion-related metadata for storage in converted files if not provided by the user.
If the user does not provide metadata related to the conversion, the system shall automatically generate metadata to be stored in the converted files.

label: The system shall automatically generate migration metadata.
